    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1963-07-16T07:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1963-07-16T07:00:00-05:00" n="222"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d222">
                <head>222. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">Embassy in Vietnam</gloss> to the
                        <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d222fn1">Source: Department of State, Central
                        Files, SOC 14-1 <gloss target="#t_S1">S</gloss> VIET. Secret; Operational
                        Immediate; Limit Distribution. Repeated to <gloss target="#t_CINCPAC1"
                            >CINCPAC</gloss>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <hi rend="italic">
                            <placeName>Saigon</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                                when="1963-07-16T20:00:00+08:00">July 16, 1963, 8 p.m.</date>
                        </hi>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>92. <gloss target="#t_CINCPAC1">CINCPAC</gloss> for <gloss target="#t_POLAD1"
                        >POLAD</gloss>. Reference: Embassy’s telegram 91.<note n="2"
                        xml:id="d222fn2">Document 221.</note> When it appeared at about 10:30 that
                    another self-immolation might be imminent, I telephoned <persName
                        corresp="#p_THUAN1">Thuan</persName> and asked him to see <persName
                        corresp="#p_DIEM1">Diem</persName> urgently. I proposed that President get
                    word to demonstrators immediately by loudspeaker truck that he would be
                    addressing people personally at a stated hour, preferably noon. Told <persName
                        corresp="#p_THUAN1">Thuan</persName> I judged we’re at eleventh hour and
                    personal action by <persName corresp="#p_DIEM1">Diem</persName> required.
                        <persName corresp="#p_THUAN1">Thuan</persName> said he agreed and would go
                    immediately to <persName corresp="#p_DIEM1">Diem</persName>. I asked to see
                        <persName corresp="#p_DIEM1">Diem</persName> myself if <persName
                        corresp="#p_THUAN1">Thuan</persName> thought it would be helpful.</p>
                <p>About 15 minutes after above call, word received that demonstration at residence
                    appeared be breaking up and Bonzes planning return to Xa Loi to commence fast. I
                    relayed this to <persName corresp="#p_THUAN1">Thuan</persName> (who had not yet
                    been able to see <persName corresp="#p_DIEM1">Diem</persName>), but told him in
                    my judgment personal address by President still urgently required. I offered
                    provide some suggestions on content and am doing so.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_NFEJ1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Nolting</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
